Package: pricesensitivitymeter
Date: 2019-xx-xx
Type: Package
Title: Van Westendorp Price Sensitivity Meter Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Max", "Alletsee", email = "max.alletsee@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Max Alletsee <max.alletsee@gmail.com>                  
Description: An implementation of the van Westendorp Price
    Sensitivity Meter in R, which is a survey-based approach
	to analyze consumer price preferences and sensitivity
    (van Westendorp 1976, isbn:9789283100386).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Encoding: UTF-8
BugReports: https://github.com/alletsee/pricesensitivitymeter/issues
URL: https://github.com/alletsee/pricesensitivitymeter
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0),
	methods
Imports: survey (>= 3.23-1)
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat,
    ggplot2
